subtemplate.unicode: Map Marker: Directional/Aggressive||Use this red, pointed marker to direct allies on an attack course.||It can be drawn directly onto the terrain or onto the radar map.
Map Marker: General||Use this blue marker for general highlighting and movement orders to your allies.||It can be drawn directly onto the terrain or onto the radar map.
Map Marker: Defensive||Use this green boxed marker to tell allies where to hold their position.||It can be drawn directly onto the terrain or onto the radar map.
